{"id":688,"parent_id":680,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":688,"title":"Ecclesiastes 8","subtitle":"","short_title":"Eccl.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 8"],[".studySummary",["i","None have power to avoid death—It will not be well with the wicked; he turns to pleasure and cannot find wisdom."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.1","order":"02.22.008.44533"},["b","1"],"Who",["i","is"],"as the wise",["i","man?"],"and who knoweth the interpretation of a thing? a man’s wisdom maketh his face to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"shine"],", and the boldness of his face shall be changed."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.2","order":"02.22.008.44534"},["b","2"],"I",["i","counsel thee"],"to keep the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"king’s"],"commandment, and",["i","that"],"in regard of the oath of God."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.3","order":"02.22.008.44535"},["b","3"],"Be not hasty to go out of his sight: stand not in an evil thing; for he doeth whatsoever pleaseth him."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.4","order":"02.22.008.44536"},["b","4"],"Where the word of a king",["i","is, there is"],"power: and who may say unto him, What doest thou?"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.5","order":"02.22.008.44537"},["b","5"],"Whoso keepeth the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"commandment"],"shall feel no evil thing: and a wise man’s heart discerneth both",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"time"],"and judgment."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.6","order":"02.22.008.44538"},["b","6"],"¶Because to every purpose there is time and judgment, therefore the misery of man",["i","is"],"great upon him."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.7","order":"02.22.008.44539"},["b","7"],"For he knoweth not that which shall be: for who can tell him when it shall be?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.8","order":"02.22.008.44540"},["b","8"],["i","There is"],"no man that hath power over the spirit to retain the spirit; neither",["i","hath he"],"power in the day of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"death"],": and",["i","there is"],"no discharge in",["i","that"],"war; neither shall wickedness",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"deliver"],"those that are given to it."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.9","order":"02.22.008.44541"},["b","9"],"All this have I seen, and applied my heart unto every work that is done under the sun:",["i","there is"],"a time wherein one man ruleth over another to his own hurt."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.10","order":"02.22.008.44542"},["b","10"],"And so I saw the wicked buried, who had come and gone from the place of the holy, and they were forgotten in the city where they had so done: this",["i","is"],"also vanity."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.11","order":"02.22.008.44543"},["b","11"],"Because sentence against an evil work is not executed",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"speedily"],", therefore the heart of the sons of men is fully",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"set"],"in them to do evil."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.12","order":"02.22.008.44544"},["b","12"],"¶Though a sinner do evil an hundred times, and his",["i","days"],"be prolonged, yet surely I know that it shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"well"],"with them that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"fear"],"God, which fear before him:"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.13","order":"02.22.008.44545"},["b","13"],"But it shall not be well with the wicked, neither shall he prolong",["i","his"],"days,",["i","which are"],"as a shadow; because he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"feareth not before God"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.14","order":"02.22.008.44546"},["b","14"],"There is a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"vanity"],"which is done upon the earth; that there be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"just"],["i","men,"],"unto whom it happeneth according to the work of the wicked; again, there be wicked",["i","men,"],"to whom it happeneth according to the work of the righteous: I said that this also",["i","is"],"vanity."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.15","order":"02.22.008.44547"},["b","15"],"Then I commended mirth, because a man hath no better thing under the sun, than to eat, and to drink, and to be merry: for that shall abide with him of his labour the days of his life, which God giveth him under the sun."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.16","order":"02.22.008.44548"},["b","16"],"¶When I applied mine heart to know",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"wisdom"],", and to see the business that is done upon the earth: (for also",["i","there is that"],"neither day nor night seeth sleep with his eyes:)"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.17","order":"02.22.008.44549"},["b","17"],"Then I beheld all the work of God, that a man cannot find out the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"work"],"that is done under the sun: because though a man labour to seek",["i","it"],"out, yet he shall not find",["i","it;"],"yea further; though a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"wise"],["i","man"],"think to know",["i","it,"],"yet shall he not be able to find",["i","it."]]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.1a","order":"02.22.008.44550"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/50.24"},"D&C 50:24"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.45"},"84:45"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.2a","order":"02.22.008.44552"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/citizenship"},"TG Citizenship"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/governments"},"Governments"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.5a","order":"02.22.008.44554"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/20.18"},"1 Ne. 20:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.5b","order":"02.22.008.44556"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/time"},"TG Time"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.8a","order":"02.22.008.44558"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.6"},"2 Ne. 9:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.8b","order":"02.22.008.44560"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/deliver"},"TG Deliver"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.11a","order":"02.22.008.44562"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/98.2"},"D&C 98:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.11b","order":"02.22.008.44564"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/8.15.13-15"},"Ex. 8:15 (13–15)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.12a","order":"02.22.008.44566"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/1.20.7-20"},"Ex. 1:20 (7–20)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.9"},"D&C 1:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.12b","order":"02.22.008.44568"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/3.10"},"Isa. 3:10"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reverence"},"TG Reverence"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.13a","order":"02.22.008.44570"},["b","13a"],["span.small","OR"],"is not reverent before God.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/44.10.10-11"},"Jer. 44:10 (10–11)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/10.56"},"D&C 10:56"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.14a","order":"02.22.008.44572"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vanity"},"TG Vanity"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.14b","order":"02.22.008.44574"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/7.15"},"Eccl. 7:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/3.14.14-18"},"Mal. 3:14 (14–18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.16a","order":"02.22.008.44576"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.26"},"D&C 1:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.68"},"42:68"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.17a","order":"02.22.008.44578"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/3.11"},"Eccl. 3:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/8.17b","order":"02.22.008.44580"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.28"},"2 Ne. 9:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.9"},"D&C 76:9"],"."]]}
